    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1942-11-12T07:35:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1942-11-12T07:35:00-05:00" n="296"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d296">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">891.24/285: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Iran</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dreyfus</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tehran</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-11-12T16:00:00+03:25"
                            >November 12, 1942—4 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received November 12—2:11 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>372. My number 364, November 9, 2 p.m.<note n="38" xml:id="d296fn38">Not
                        printed.</note> Majlis today passed law for employment of Millspaugh. Prime
                    Minister urges that he come forward as soon as possible since important
                    financial legislation will be suspended pending his arrival.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Dreyfus</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
